  "subject": "7.0.0 release",
  "commit_message": "7.0.0 release\n\n- reimplementation in go\n- statically compiled and thus much\n  faster to launch\n- smaller image size (109MB -> 42MB)\n- distroless base image, thus having no\n  OS level dependencies that could become vulnerable\n- app-name, container-name and service-mesh-check are\n  not supported anymore [0]\n\n[0] service-mesh-check is obsolete since istio native\n    sidecars are used. app- and container-name args are\n    removed since the same can be achieved with pod-name\n    and service-name\n\nIssue-ID: INT-2331\nChange-Id: I3bfd82dac494ff57aef3a9804970704b5413ff4c\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
